<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8" />
	<title>매장 선택 - GS Retail</title>
	<meta name="viewport" content="user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, width=device-width, target-densitydpi=medium-dpi" />
	<meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no,address=no,email=no" />
	<meta name="description" contents=""/>
	<meta name="keywords" contents=""/>
	<link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" href="../images/favicon/favicon.ico">
	<link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="../images/favicon/favicon.png">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/common.css">
	<script src="../../js/jquery-1.12.4.min.js"></script>
	<script src="../../js/plugin.js"></script>
	<script src="../../js/common.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
	<!-- fullpop :: 매장 선택 -->
	<div id="pop01" class="fullPop gs25">
		<h1>매장 선택</h1>
		<div class="popCon">
			<div class="tabArea">
				<ul role="tablist">
					<li><a href="#" role="tab" aria-selected="false">현재위치</a></li>
					<li><a href="#" role="tab" aria-selected="true">단골/최근이용</a></li>
					<li><a href="#" role="tab" aria-selected="false">매장명/지역별</a></li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div class="tabCont findStore">
				<div class="storeHistory">
					<div class="titArea">
						<h2 class="titDep1">단골 매장<span class="sub">(<em class="color01">3</em>개)</span></h2>
					</div>
					<ul class="storeList simple">
						<li><a href="#" role="button" data-path="pathStore" title="매장 선택"><strong class="tit">GS THE FRESH 도곡렉슬점</strong><span class="txt">서울 강남구 선릉로 225, 상가 지하 1층(도곡렉스점)</span></a></li>
						<li><a href="#" role="button" data-path="pathStore" title="매장 선택"><strong class="tit">GS THE FRESH 도곡렉슬점</strong><span class="txt">서울 강남구 선릉로 225, 상가 지하 1층</span></a></li>
						<li><a href="#" role="button" data-path="pathStore" title="매장 선택"><strong class="tit">GS THE FRESH 도곡렉슬점</strong><span class="txt">서울 강남구 선릉로 225, 상가 지하 1층</span></a></li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="storeHistory line">
					<div class="titArea">
						<h2 class="titDep1">최근이용 매장<span class="sub">(<em class="color01">1</em>개)</span></h2>
					</div>
					<ul class="storeList simple">
						<li><a href="#" role="button" title="매장 선택"><strong class="tit">GS THE FRESH 도곡렉슬점</strong><span class="txt">서울 강남구 선릉로 225, 상가 지하 1층</span></a></li>
					</ul>
					<!-- 단골매장/최근이용 모두 없을 경우 -->
					<div class="noData">
						<p class="desc">등록된 매장이 없습니다.</p>
						<p>현재위치/매장명/지역별 찾기를 이용하여 매장을 선택해주세요.</p>
					</div>
					<!-- //단골매장/최근이용 모두 없을 경우 -->
				</div>
				<!-- 드로어 : 선택 매장 -->
				<div id="pathStore" class="layDrawer">
					<div class="drwTit">
						<h2 class="tit">선택 매장</h2>
						<button type="button" class="close">닫기</button>
					</div>
					<div class="drwCon">
						<p class="storeInfo">
							<strong class="tit"><em role="text" class="icoStar">단골매장</em>GS25 역삼행복점A</strong><span class="txt">서울 강남구 역삼동 778-6번지 1층 2호</span>
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="btnFixed">
						<div class="btnPrss">
							<button type="button" class="btnTP active">선택완료</button>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<!-- //드로어 : 선택 매장 -->
			</div>
		</div>
		<button type="button" class="btnClose">팝업 닫기</button>
	</div>
	<!-- //fullpop :: 매장 선택 -->
</body>
</html>